class ListNode {
    int val;
    ListNode next;

    ListNode(int val) {
        this.val = val;
        this.next = null;
    }
}

public class MiddleOfLinkedList {

    public static ListNode middleNode(ListNode head) {
        ListNode slow = head;
        ListNode fast = head;

        while (fast != null && fast.next != null) {
            slow = slow.next;       // moves 1 step
            fast = fast.next.next;  // moves 2 steps
        }
        return slow; // slow reaches middle
    }
}
In a linked list, returning a node returns the rest of the list from that node.
